{"pin":"AB10714","subcodes":[{"code":"AB10714","anchor":"","first_line":"O Thou kind Lord! These lovely children are the handiwork of the fingers of Thy might and the wondrous signs of Thy greatness.","first_line_orig":"خداوندا مهربانا این اطفال نازنین صنع دست قدرت تو است و ایات عظمت تو خدایا این  ","language":"Per","word_count":"60","subjects":"@prayer for children and youth, @education of children; moral education","full_text_parts":["O Thou kind Lord! These lovely children are the handiwork of the fingers of Thy might and the wondrous signs of Thy greatness. O God! Protect these children, graciously assist them to be educated and enable them to render service to the world of humanity. O God! These children are pearls, cause them to be nurtured within the shell of Thy loving-kindness.\n\nThou art the Bountiful, the All-Loving."],"translations":[{"language":"hy","lang_name":"Armenian"},{"language":"tet","lang_name":"Tetum"},{"language":"ru","lang_name":"Russian"},{"language":"bg","lang_name":"Bulgarian"},{"language":"fr","lang_name":"French"},{"language":"az","lang_name":"Azerbaijani"},{"language":"lt","lang_name":"Lithuanian"},{"language":"iba","lang_name":"Iban"},{"language":"ht","lang_name":"Haitian Creole"},{"language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"language":"ky","lang_name":"Kirghiz"},{"language":"ta","lang_name":"Tamil"},{"language":"fa","lang_name":"Persian"},{"language":"ml","lang_name":"Malayalam"},{"language":"de","lang_name":"German"},{"language":"nl","lang_name":"Dutch"},{"language":"th","lang_name":"Thai"},{"language":"el","lang_name":"Greek"},{"language":"sk","lang_name":"Slovak"},{"language":"tl","lang_name":"Tagalog"},{"language":"ca","lang_name":"Catalan"},{"language":"da","lang_name":"Danish"},{"language":"pt","lang_name":"Portuguese"},{"language":"es","lang_name":"Spanish"},{"language":"mn","lang_name":"Mongolian"},{"language":"hu","lang_name":"Hungarian"},{"language":"zh-Hans","lang_name":"Simplified Chinese"},{"language":"be","lang_name":"Belar